<!DOCTYPE html>
<html {{ site.language_attributes }}>


    {% include 'html-header.twig' %}

    <body id="body_wrapper">
    {% include "navbar.twig" %}
        {% block content %}
            <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid mb-0" style="height: 400px!important; background-image: url('{{ webInfo.baeurl }}/app/themes/fid-phil/assets/img/a_school.jpg'); background-position: center">
                <div class="container" style="margin-top: 50px!important;">
                    <div class="card border-0">
                        <form method="get" action="/">
                            <div class="card-header p-0 border-0">
                                <div id="search_wrapper" class="input-group input-group-lg shadow-sm" >
                                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                        <button type="submit" class="input-group-text bg-fid border-fid" >
                                            <i class="fas fa-search text-white"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                    <input id="freetext-input" type="text" name="freetext" class="form-control" placeholder="Suche..." required>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="extendedSearch" class="collapse ">
                                <div  class="card-body border-fid d-md-block d-none">
                                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center" style="width: 100%">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between bg-white" style="height: 150px!important; width: 95%">
                                            <div class="card border-fid-secondary" style="width: 20%">
                                                <div class="card-header p-1 bg-white">
                                                    <h6 class="text-center">Suchbereich:</h6>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="card-body p-1">
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">KUG/BVB</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">Philosophers Index</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="card border-fid-tertiary" style="width: 20%">
                                                <div class="card-header p-1 bg-white">
                                                    <h6 class="text-center">Zugriff:</h6>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="card-body p-1">
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">Volltextzugriff</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">kein Volltextzugriff</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">beides</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="card border-fid-secondary" style="width: 20%">
                                                <div class="card-header p-1 bg-white">
                                                    <h6 class="text-center">Medientyp:</h6>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="card-body p-1">
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">Monografien</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">Zeitungsartikel</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="custom-control custom-checkbox">
                                                        <input type="checkbox" class="custom-control-input" id="customCheck" name="example1">
                                                        <label class="custom-control-label" for="customCheck">Online</label>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="card border-fid-tertiary" style="width: 20%">
                                                <div class="card-header p-1 bg-white">
                                                    <h6 class="text-center">Erscheinungsjahr:</h6>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="card-body p-1">
                                                    <div id="steps-slider"></div>
                                                    <input type="number" id="input-with-keypress-0">
                                                    <input type="number" id="input-with-keypress-1">
                                                </div>
                                                <script>
                                                    var stepsSlider = document.getElementById('steps-slider');
                                                    var input0 = document.getElementById('input-with-keypress-0');
                                                    var input1 = document.getElementById('input-with-keypress-1');
                                                    var inputs = [input0, input1];

                                                    noUiSlider.create(stepsSlider, {
                                                        start: [0, 2020],
                                                        connect: true,
                                                        tooltips: [true, wNumb({decimals: 0})],
                                                        range: {
                                                            'min': [0, 100],
                                                            '40%': [1900, 10],
                                                            '75%':[2010, 1],
                                                            'max': 2020
                                                        }
                                                    });

                                                    stepsSlider.noUiSlider.on('update', function (values, handle) {
                                                        inputs[handle].value = values[handle];
                                                    });
                                                </script>
                                            </div>


                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </form>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-md-flex justify-content-end d-none bg-transparent" style="width: 95%">
                        <div class="align-self-end">
                            <button type="button" class="input-group-text bg-fid border-fid text-white" style="border-top-right-radius: 0!important; border-top-left-radius: 0!important;" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#extendedSearch">
                                <small><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Sucheinstellungen</small>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center d-md-none">
                        <button class="btn btn-fid" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#extendedSearchModal" style="border-top-right-radius: 0!important; border-top-left-radius: 0!important;"><i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i> Erweiterte Suche</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="height: 3px; margin-top: 0!important; padding-top: 0!important;">
            <div class="modal" id="extendedSearchModal">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                    <div class="modal-content">

                        <!-- Modal Header -->
                        <div class="modal-header">
                            <h4 class="modal-title">Modal Heading</h4>
                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Modal body -->
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            Modal body..
                        </div>

                        <!-- Modal footer -->
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="short_desc" class="container p-5">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-md-around text-white">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="card landing-card bg-fid border-0 shadow">
                            <div class="card-header d-flex flex-column"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap icon-fid align-self-center"></i><h3 class="align-self-center">Registrieren</h3></div>
                            <div class="card-body landing-tile-font">Registrieren und Zugang zu über 5.000.000 Monografien und 3.000.000 Zeitschriften zum Themenschwerpunkt Philosophie erhalten. Mitglieder von Fachgesellschaften können darüberhinaus Volltexte aus dem Philosopher's Index nutzen</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="card landing-card bg-fid-secondary border-0 shadow" >
                            <div class="card-header d-flex flex-column"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram align-self-center"></i><h3 class="align-self-center text-center">Kuration</h3></div>
                            <div class="card-body pt-0 landing-tile-font">Kuratierte Zugänge geben einen Überblick zu einzelnen Themen und AutorInnen</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="card landing-card bg-fid-tertiary border-0 shadow">
                            <div class="card-header d-flex flex-column"><i class="fas fa-align-justify align-self-center"></i><h3 class="align-self-center">Volltexte</h3></div>
                            <div class="card-body landing-tile-font">Die DigiPhiD werden ständig Monografien und Sammelbände retrodigitalisiert. Der Bestand soll bis 2022 auf 300.000 Seiten ausgebaut werden</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="height: 3px; margin-bottom: 0!important; padding-bottom: 0!important;">
            <div id="long_desc"  style="width: 100%">
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 bg-light p-5" style="height: 50vh">
                        <h2 class="text-center">Fachinformationsdienst</h2>
